{
  "texts": [
    "Safe management and maintenance of equipment are critical, but neglecting both can lead to problems, deterioration, and reduced harvesting efficiency (Duckett et al. 2018).",
    "In addition, the complexity of the equipment can lead to high maintenance costs and operator difficulties (Ampatzidis et al. 2014).",
    "Therefore, it is urgent to accelerate the development towards automation, intelligence, and user-friendliness so that harvesting equipment can be developed in the direction of simple operation, low failure rate, safety, and reliability.",
    "In view of the above problems, automatic fruit harvesting machinery is one of the difficulties and hot spots in the field of agricultural high technology.",
    "Its harvesting efficiency has been a difficult problem for researchers."
  ]
}